1. 	do install npm first
2. 	npm init ( select default option)
3. 	npm install angular (or other dependancy)
4. 	create index.html
5. 	include angular path in html page
6. 	create app folder
7. 	create app.js in app folder
8. 	define module in app.js
9. 	include app.js in index.html 
10. create controllers folder and create demo.ctrl.js and include in index.html (be sure should be include 	    after app.js)
11. create $scope variable and show in html page



create Services-service:
	1. create folder services, add service file,create service method and include in html page and
	2. Include service name in controller
	3. use controller by service name


